      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      199.46,
      146.71,
      212.42
    ],
    "text": "Sri.L.R. 384].",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      223.34,
      544.29,
      236.3
    ],
    "text": "Nevertheless, in my view, the Cabinet decision itself is not the act which, as has been",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      247.13,
      544.3,
      260.09
    ],
    "text": "alleged, would constitute an infringement of the fundamental rights of Petitioners. It is",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      270.89,
      543.9,
      283.85
    ],
    "text": "only when the Attorney-General, if he chooses to do so, acts on the impugned Cabinet",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      294.77,
      544.21,
      307.73
    ],
    "text": "decision that there may be, as alleged, an infringement of the fundamental rights of the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      318.53,
      135.91,
      331.49
    ],
    "text": "Petitioners.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      342.29,
      544.04,
      355.25
    ],
    "text": "This court has recognized the notion of a continuing violation of fundamental rights",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      366.17,
      544.2,
      379.13
    ],
    "text": "[Wijesekera and Others v. Attorney-General (2007) 1 Sri.L.R. 38; Sugathapala Mendis and",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      389.93,
      544.22,
      402.89
    ],
    "text": "Another v. Chandrika Kumaratunga and Others (Waters Edge case) (2008) 2 Sri.L.R. 339;",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      413.71,
      543.75,
      426.67
    ],
    "text": "Wijesekera and 14 Others v. Gamini Lokuge, Minister of Sports and Public Recreation and",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      437.59,
      244.78,
      450.55
    ],
    "text": "20 Others (2011) 2 Sri.L.R. 329].",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      461.35,
      544.31,
      474.31
    ],
    "text": "In my view, there are situations where imminent infringements are also continuing. As a",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      485.23,
      544.18,
      498.19
    ],
    "text": "matter of fact, by definition, imminent infringements continue until a fundamental right",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      508.99,
      541.31,
      521.95
    ],
    "text": "is violated or the decision-maker changes his or her mind. Hence until the Attorney-",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      532.75,
      544.31,
      545.71
    ],
    "text": "General acts on the Cabinet decision or there is a change of mind of the Cabinet, the acts",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      556.63,
      544.32,
      569.59
    ],
    "text": "impugned by the Petitioners are allegedly continuing imminent infringements of the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      580.42,
      544.05,
      593.38
    ],
    "text": "fundamental rights of the Petitioners. Accordingly, I conclude that the amended petition",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      604.18,
      357.0,
      617.14
    ],
    "text": "is not time barred and overrule the second objection.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      628.06,
      543.77,
      641.02
    ],
    "text": "The third objection is that the amended petition has been filed to cure the defects in the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      651.82,
      547.37,
      664.78
    ],
    "text": "original petition which were brought to the notice of Court on behalf of the Respondents.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      675.58,
      544.32,
      688.54
    ],
    "text": "No doubt the Petitioners have included several new prayers in the amended petition. They",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      699.46,
      544.33,
      712.42
    ],
    "text": "have also pleaded the Cabinet decision taken on the Cabinet Memorandum [P10] in",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      723.22,
      515.55,
      736.18
    ],
    "text": "addition to making all the members of the Cabinet Respondents to the application.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      282.05,
      781.32,
      333.89,
      792.36
    ],
    "text": "Page 5 of 6",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      56.64,
      544.35,
      69.6
    ],
    "text": "Nonetheless, this is a fundamental rights application filed in the public interest. The",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      80.42,
      543.9,
      93.38
    ],
    "text": "Petitioners allege that the impugned Cabinet Memorandum and decision are an attempt",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      104.3,
      543.82,
      117.26
    ],
    "text": "at political interference of national legislation and violation /an imminent threat of",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      128.06,
      544.32,
      141.02
    ],
    "text": "violation of the Fauna and Flora Protection Ordinance. It is further submitted that there",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      151.82,
      326.64,
      164.78
    ],
    "text": "is a breach/imminent breach of the rule of law.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      175.7,
      543.71,
      188.66
    ],
    "text": "Whilst the Cabinet Memorandum sought approval of the Cabinet Ministers to withdraw",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      199.46,
      543.86,
      212.42
    ],
    "text": "all cases where legal action is being taken at present and to hand over these animals to",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      223.34,
      544.05,
      236.3
    ],
    "text": "their present owners according to the conditions of transferring these animals, the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      247.13,
      543.91,
      260.09
    ],
    "text": "Cabinet decision is to direct the Secretary, Ministry of Wildlife & Forest Conservation to",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      270.89,
      543.81,
      283.85
    ],
    "text": "bring the special reasons adduced in the Memorandum to the notice of the Attorney",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      294.77,
      544.0,
      307.73
    ],
    "text": "General and thereafter take necessary action in association with the Secretary, Ministry",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      318.53,
      543.74,
      331.49
    ],
    "text": "of Public Security and in consultation with the Attorney General to reach an amicable",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      342.29,
      543.83,
      355.25
    ],
    "text": "settlement with the relevant parties pertaining to the pending court cases, giving due",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      366.17,
      511.59,
      379.13
    ],
    "text": "consideration to the proposal (4.2) in paragraph 4.0 of the Cabinet Memorandum.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      389.93,
      544.35,
      402.89
    ],
    "text": "In Attorney-General (on the relation of McWhirter) v. Independent Broadcasting Authority",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      413.71,
      544.16,
      426.67
    ],
    "text": "[(1973) 1 All ER 689 at 697] Lord Denning succinctly described the role of the Attorney",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      437.59,
      237.22,
      450.55
    ],
    "text": "General of England as follows:",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      468.91,
      543.81,
      481.87
    ],
    "text": "It is settled in our constitutional law that in matters which , concern the public at",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      492.67,
      543.92,
      505.63
    ],
    "text": "large the Attorney-General is the guardian of the public interest. Although he is a",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      516.43,
      544.19,
      529.39
    ],
    "text": "member of the government of the day, it is his duty to represent the public interest",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      540.31,
      543.81,
      553.27
    ],
    "text": "with complete objectivity and detachment. He must act independently of any",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      564.07,
      543.74,
      577.03
    ],
    "text": "external pressure from . whatever quarter it may come. As the guardian of the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      587.98,
      544.35,
      600.94
    ],
    "text": "public interest, the Attorney-General has a special duty in regard to the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      611.74,
      339.24,
      624.7
    ],
    "text": "enforcement of the law.\" [emphasis added]",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      644.5,
      544.17,
      657.46
    ],
    "text": "Although there may be some differences in the two roles, these observations aptly apply",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      668.38,
      544.21,
      681.34
    ],
    "text": "to the role of the Attorney-General of Sri Lanka. In fact, in Land Reform Commission v.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      692.14,
      544.27,
      705.1
    ],
    "text": "Grand Central Limited [(1981) 1 Sri.L.R. 250] this Court held that the Attorney-General has",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      715.9,
      543.81,
      728.86
    ],
    "text": "a duty to the Court, to the State and to the subject to be wholly detached, wholly",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      739.8,
      501.63,
      752.76
    ],
    "text": "independent and to act impartially with the sole object of establishing the truth.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      282.05,
      781.32,
      333.89,
      792.36
    ],
    "text": "Page 6 of 6",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      56.64,
      544.09,
      69.6
    ],
    "text": "The Attorney-General is vested with extensive statutory powers in relation to criminal",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      80.42,
      544.3,
      93.38
    ],
    "text": "investigations and prosecutions. Such powers are held in public trust. They must be",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      104.3,
      544.3,
      117.26
    ],
    "text": "exercised for the due administration of justice according to the rule of law which is the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      128.06,
      543.97,
      141.02
    ],
    "text": "basis of our Constitution. Any type of dictation from whatever quarter will compromise",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      151.82,
      544.31,
      164.78
    ],
    "text": "the independence of the Attorney-General unless such dictation is permitted by law. Any",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      175.7,
      544.24,
      188.66
    ],
    "text": "compromise of the independence of the Attorney-General will have a negative impact on",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      198.23,
      544.29,
      212.42
    ],
    "text": "the rule of law. The heart of the Petitioners' complaint is that the 1st and 2nd Respondents",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.520000457763672,
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      223.34,
      544.22,
      236.3
    ],
    "text": "and the Cabinet of Ministers are interfering with the statutory powers of the Attorney",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      247.13,
      122.83,
      260.09
    ],
    "text": "General.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      279.89,
      544.28,
      292.85
    ],
    "text": "This is a serious allegation, which if true, has far reaching ramifications. According to",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      303.77,
      544.2,
      316.73
    ],
